ESP32C3 TR-808 Drum Machine Library License Notice

This library provides an implementation of the Roland TR-808 drum machine
algorithm for ESP32C3 microcontrollers. The TR-808 is a legendary drum
machine originally manufactured by Roland Corporation.

TR-808 is a trademark of Roland Corporation. This software library is not
affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Roland Corporation.

The algorithmic synthesis techniques used in this library are based on:
1. Publicly available research papers and technical documentation
2. Reverse engineering efforts by the audio synthesis community
3. Creative Commons and open source references

This library aims to provide educational value and hobbyist enjoyment while
respecting the intellectual property rights of original designers.

For commercial use of TR-808 sounds, please consult with Roland Corporation
or use licensed samples from authorized providers.

Original TR-808 was manufactured by:
Roland Corporation
2036-1 Nakacho, Hamamatsu-shi
Shizuoka-ken, 433-8114, Japan
https://www.roland.com/

