Version History

v1.0.0 (2025-10-30)
- Initial release
- Complete TR-808 drum synthesis implementation
- ESP32C3 optimization
- Real-time I2S audio output
- Comprehensive documentation and examples

Future versions will maintain backward compatibility when possible and
follow semantic versioning principles.

